title: TTC Invisible Clone using One Bob-omb and No Explosion Clones

media:group.media:title: TTC Invisible Clone using One Bob-omb and No Explosion Clones
media:group.media:description: I show that we can achieve an invisible clone (without modifying the HOLP) using just one bob-omb and no explosion clones in TTC. This strat is an improvement from the previous strat that used 3 explosion clones to do the same thing (https://youtu.be/HQo50BmkKGA). Since then, I figured out a way to use behind camera anywhere to replace the pause-buffered hitstun. Thus, this strat should save time and object slots.
